#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.215"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.215:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.215:0.2"
msgid "22. Akkosakavagga"
msgstr "22. Abuse"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.215:0.3"
msgid "215. Paṭhamaakkhantisutta"
msgstr "215. Intolerance (1st)"

# BB has “impatience”. but it is hard to see why you might go to hell for being impatient!
#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.215:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā akkhantiyā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks of intolerance."

msgctxt "an5.215:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.215:1.3"
msgid ""
"Bahuno janassa appiyo hoti amanāpo, verabahulo ca hoti, vajjabahulo ca, "
"sammūḷho kālaṃ karoti, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ "
"nirayaṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"Most people find you unlikable and unloveable. You have lots of enmity and "
"many flaws. You feel lost when you die. And when your body breaks up, after "
"death, you’re reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "an5.215:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā akkhantiyā."
msgstr "These are the five drawbacks to intolerance."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.215:2.1"
msgid "Pañcime, bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā khantiyā."
msgstr "There are these five benefits of tolerance."

msgctxt "an5.215:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.215:2.3"
msgid ""
"Bahuno janassa piyo hoti manāpo, na verabahulo hoti, na vajjabahulo, "
"asammūḷho kālaṃ karoti, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ "
"upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"Most people find you dear and lovable. You have little enmity and few flaws. "
"You don’t feel lost when you die. And when your body breaks up, after death, "
"you’re reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm."

msgctxt "an5.215:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ānisaṃsā khantiyā”ti."
msgstr "These are the five benefits of tolerance.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.215:2.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
